</p><p style=3D"color: rgb(54, 55, 55); font-size: 16px; line-height: 26px;=
 margin: 0 0 20px 0;">Well, teleportation might not be the exact right term=
=2E Here&#8217;s how it works: Osmo cre=
ated a &quot;Principal Odor Map&quot;=20=
that can predict how a molecule will smell based solely on its chemical str=
ucture. This allows them to digitally explore billions of potential molecul=
es and predict their scents without physically synthesizing them, greatly a=
ccelerating the process of discovering new fragrances and aroma compounds. =
The POM then generates a formula to recreate the scent, sends the formula t=
o a specialized printer, which then uses a combination of scent ingredients=
 to &#8220;print&#8221; the smell. Watch the video above to get a better id=
ea of how it works.</p><p style=3D"color: rgb(54, 55, 55); font-size: 16px;=
 line-height: 26px; margin: 0 0 20px 0;">Vision and hearing have been digit=
